A collection of helpful automations for your projects directory

****************************************
* upproj 
****************************************

Simplify (read: automate) the maintenance of a project aliases file 
reads your project directory and creates an alias for each folder name therein
run upproj and simple type a project folder name to immediately cd to that folder

Usage: upproj 

	########
		REQUIRED CONFIG
			see projects_path.txt
				place here path to your projects directory
				
****************************************
* clean_dw_trash 
****************************************

Simplify (read: automate) the removal of the _notes folders that DreamWeaver likes to put in every single stinking folder of a dreamweaver project

Usage: clean_dw_trash 

